" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Recovery from diaphragmatic fatigue",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 439px; height: 277px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Induction of diaphragmatic fatigue (red bar) produced a significant fall in transdiaphragmatic twitch pressure (Pditw). Nadir of Pditw was reached 10 minutes after conclusion of fatigue protocol, and PDitw values at 8 and 24 hours remained lower than baseline (BL). Significant difference compared with BL value, p &lt; 0.01.",
